Revision history for Alien-pugixml

0.03  2026-06-25
    - Source build updated to pugixml 1.16
    - Require pugixml >= 1.8 for system detection

0.02  2026-03-04
    - Add CI for Linux, macOS, FreeBSD
    - Fix repository metadata

0.01  2026-01-22
    - Initial release
    - Provides pugixml 1.15 C++ XML parser library
    - Supports system detection via pkg-config
    - Share install builds static library with CMake
